</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="33.[151,1437,1340,1619]" box="[199,561,1592,1619]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,386,1592,1619]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Activity period.</emphasis>
